  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0b95\u0bc1\u0bb4\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bb1\u0bc8\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0ba8\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc8 \u0ba8\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0bb5\u0b95\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0baa\u0ba4\u0bb5\u0bbf \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0b95\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bbe\u0bb1\u0bc1 \u0b9c\u0ba9\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0b90\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbf\u0baf \u0bae\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0b95\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf \u0bb5\u0bb2\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bc1\u0bb1\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bb2\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "United People's Shakti urges the President to hide in a bunker and resign without governing the country",
      "author": "Digital Desk 5",
      "body_lines": [
        "The government has bypassed the media in fuel distribution only to silence them. This kind of media suppression will be done in front of united people. Member of Parliament Ranjith Mathuma Bandara said that he urges President Gotabaya Rajapaksa to step down instead of running the country from hiding in bunkers.",
        "He disclosed this at a press conference held on Sunday (03) at the Office of the Leader of the Opposition in Colombo, further stating,",
        "On May 11, President Gotabaya Rajapaksa promised to re-implement the 19th constitutional amendment as requested by the people.",
        "He also mentioned that the executive presidential system will be abolished. But currently the 22nd constitutional amendment submitted by the government is seen as increasing the powers of the President as compared to the 19th.",
        "President Gotabaya Rajapaksa is deceiving the people. The Gotabaya-Ranil Wickramasinghe government is not an all-party government.",
        "It is because of this that the Maha Sangh has insisted on the formation of a proper all-party government. But President Gotabaya Rajapaksa is still clutching his stick like an idiot.",
        "If he continues in office for two more years as he mentioned, people will die without food and medicine. Currently, the government has taken measures to block the media.",
        "It is because of this that the media is not included in essential services and is not fueled by them. United People's Power will act against repression against the media.",
        "We call on all political parties to oust the government involved in such improper activities and form an all-party government.",
        "He also said that we are urging President Gotabaya Rajapaksa to step down instead of running the country from hiding in bunkers."
      ],
